s around the world we believe that our broad diversification in combination with our proprietary technology platform and lowcost structure enables us to facilitate risk transfer between global capital markets participants by supplying liquidity and competitive pricing while at the same time earning attractive margins and returns why virtu financial more than  securities and other financial instruments on more than  unique exchanges markets and liquidity pools in  countries around the world acquisitions press release rss feed opens in new window press releases jul   virtu financial to host conference call announcing  second quarter results on tuesday august   view more jul   virtu financial inc completes acquisition of kcg holdings inc view more jun   instinet and virtu financial launch liquidity streaming relationship pdf format download opens in new window view more all press releases quarterly financials view all reports events rss feed opens in new window events upcoming events past events aug   virtu financial conference call announcing  second quarter results add to apple calendar opens in new window add to google calendar opens in new window add to microsoft outlook opens in new window add to icalendar opens in new window webcast opens in new window view all events quarterly financials view all reports featured presentation social feed twitter quick links dividend history rss faqs email alerts email address  mailing lists  press release sec filings events  presentation eod stock price financial reports   enter the code shown above  investor contact have a specific question or request feel free to fill out the form below and we will respond as soon as we can request information contact us have a question get in touch with us work here view our job openings view locations careers  our culture  open positions  internships about market making customized liquidity history transparency locations media news comment letters   virtu financial llc all rights reserved pr